Maybe you’ve been furloughed, or you’re being extra careful with money in these uncertain times.
Identify and learn about all your shrubs and trees; online experts such as the Plant Clinic can help.
Learn about your plants as individual species, so you can understand what each one needs.
Prune shrubs according to each species’ needs.
Consider whether all your plants are in the right place in your yard, or if you should move or get rid of some.